{"tid":435752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2 年前執到銀包，交去警署，失主去領回，但比警察取走了現金","createTime":"2017-10-14T14:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T17:07:15.000Z","uid":20058,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d53b9c83e53af2c666f1a61b8977a3908776d9ea","tid":435752,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺今晚 6 時半左右，<br />\n在屯門康麗花園執到 一 個黑色銀包，<br />\n內有現金 $ 1350 元，<br />\n身份證 一 張，<br />\n八達通 一 張！<br />\n如果明天 及 後天，失主冇聯絡我，<br />\n我就會交去屯門警署！<br />\n因為 2 年前，<br />\n我執到銀包，交去警署，<br />\n失主去領回，但比警察取走了現金，<br />\n因為我曾經放過上網，<br />\n失主知道我有交出銀包內的現金，<br />\n所以失主追究，<br />\n結果該名警察又衰左！<br />\n所以，<br />\n我希望最好不用交去警署！<br />\n失主郭先生快啲睇到此 Post ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tuenmungoodlife/posts/1733226293355850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftuenmungoodlife%2Fposts%2F1733226293355850&d=LJ0OsMO7ShOGPDpPXpSF2DQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=1ace550d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tuenmungoodlife/posts/1733226293355850</a>"},{"pid":"d2e1f1162140c6bd050639b32841677c7e9524b6","tid":435752,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 警賊你都信"},{"pid":"6feff88b096d0e017bb39f23407d0cfaa7696b91","tid":435752,"uid":118827,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:43:11.000Z","msg":"又有警超聯睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8324d56a6ee69bba177118717af11db8e91f1f51","tid":435752,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"不如畀番差人收片la<br />\n成日覺得佢地唔夠駛咁，好可憐"},{"pid":"e7563c400c9fe60c7f115c4800763afaccbeb924","tid":435752,"uid":58147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:56:41.000Z","msg":"香港警察，剎無赦。"},{"pid":"388429eb9ec45f012d1ace57db1